{
  "stem": "3103.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But when I came back, I couldn't eat myself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So if there is a potato, because there were no potatoes available for us kids, I had to split with all the kids.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they laughed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They looked for Sunday, forward, for me to go and come back with one or two cookies, so we each one can have a little triangle from it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say maybe 20 slept in the same room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the time, was 13 years old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were clean.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have to admit one thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The laundry kept us supplied with-- we all wear the same clothes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we changed our clothes at least three times a week.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We wear, basically a-- in the winter, we had those [INAUDIBLE], the high-- the high boots, or else you couldn't walk in them, and coats, warm coats.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in the summer, we wore a skirt and a blouse.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the skirts and the colors used to change off.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they knew what grade is wearing what color.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to keep spotless, that place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We took turn of washing that big floor, which I had no idea how to do, but it gave me a great school.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It gave me discipline.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Once a week, we had to clean the toilets.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had to clean the-- wash the floor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Besides this, we had things to do over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They had their own farms.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And after schooling, we had to work on those farms, which it meant everything from picking potatoes to attending to cattle in the morning.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Whatever a farm is needed, the kids were doing it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Comparing at home?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Doesn't even compare.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, it's-- I tell you one episode, also.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I started school there, I went to school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I started fifth grade.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
